list_command.name: help
list_command.description: Provides all the commands available in the bot

list_command.name: ban
list_command.description: Bans mentioned users with a specified duration and reason

list_command.name: unban
list_command.description: Unbans users with a specified reason

list_command.name: level
list_command.description: Shows the level of the user or the mentioned person

list_command.name: level-give
list_command.description: Grants XP or levels to a user

list_command.name: level-remove
list_command.description: Removes XP or levels from a user

list_command.name: level-top
list_command.description: Shows the top 3 users with the highest levels

list_command.name: money
list_command.description: Displays the money of the user or the mentioned person

list_command.name: eco-top
list_command.description: Shows the top 3 users with the most money
